OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank of England insists    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fagain pensions help will   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fend                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England has insisted again 
OL,6, that it will go ahead with its decision
OL,7, to stop supporting the bond market on  
OL,8, Friday after reports it may extend it. 
OL,10,F"As it had made clear from the outset",
OL,11,Fthe help would end on Friday, it said. 
OL,13,FThe Bank is buying bonds to stabilise  
OL,14,Ftheir price and prevent a sale which   
OL,15,Fcould put some pension schemes at risk.
OL,17,FThe Bank's statement comes after boss  
OL,18,FAndrew Bailey told pension funds:      
OL,19,F"You've got three days left now and    
OL,20,Fyou've got to sort it out."            
